-- Erste Group keeps outlook, posts 9-month loss 
-- By Michael Shields
-- Thu Oct 30, 2014 02:48AM EDT
-- None



VIENNA, Oct 30 (Reuters) - Erste Group Bank <ERST.VI> swung to a nine-month loss of 1.48 billion euros ($1.86 billion) and reiterated on Thursday it expected a record loss this year.

Erste had warned in July that hits from Hungary and Romania would push it to a 2014 net loss of up to 1.6 billion euros. [ID:nL6N0PE52Q]